{"tid":120183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國有一間酒吧所有酒客打架","createTime":"2017-02-14T09:11:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-14T12:44:40.000Z","uid":55981,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"89ec373ba49beae59f81fa27f57cdcbaffb2ac19","tid":120183,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T09:11:50.000Z","msg":"英國威爾特郡（Wiltshire）一間酒吧，周日凌晨發生大規模打鬥，近100名酒客突然互相推撞和打架，警員到場嘗試阻止，但同樣被打傷臉部。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170214/large/1487039718_d753.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170214%2Flarge%2F1487039718_d753.jpg&h=e77cf231&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n21歲的阿克爾（Tommy Arkle）拍下當晚情況，他最先聽到有人大叫，又指有有一群人喝醉，「先有兩個人對一個人，突然擴大至酒吧內的每個人&hellip;&hellip;我看到人人都打架，我沒有時間去思考發生甚麼事。」<br />\n阿克爾指一位朋友被玻璃樽打爆頭受傷，「他流了很多血，額頭有個大傷口，有人叫救護車，救護車很快到場，他被送到急症室。」從片段所見酒吧內幾乎人人都有參與打鬥，互相揮拳，場面混亂。<br />\n警方就呼籲目擊者提供線索，又指一人因藏有利器被捕。<br />\n英國《每日鏡報》  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mFmrm2fqnBs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmFmrm2fqnBs&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVD54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=080fef76\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mFmrm2fqnBs</a>"},{"pid":"aabf9bfa11fe481901c4ba3a3a70ce37b7995dba","tid":120183,"uid":37933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T09:12:38.000Z","msg":"kingsman?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a74cb78bc64040c1e765b52d47d890b64012c69e","tid":120183,"uid":28256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T09:12:59.000Z","msg":"Fight Club <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f7cc9bc2c7fe24711f7d56fcf8832682dd76c4b","tid":120183,"uid":7915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T09:14:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>kingsman?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class